Package com.amplifyframework.core.model.temporal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GsonTemporalAdapters
    Collection of serializers and deserializers for AWS AppSync temporal scalars.
    GsonTemporalAdapters.DateAdapter
    Adapter for Temporal.Date, an extended ISO-8601 Date string, with an optional timezone offset.
    GsonTemporalAdapters.DateTimeAdapter
    Adapter for Temporal.DateTime, an extended ISO-8601 DateTime string.
    GsonTemporalAdapters.JavaDateAdapter
    Earlier versions of the model gen used to use Java's Date to represent all of the temporal types.
    GsonTemporalAdapters.TimeAdapter
    Adapter for Temporal.Time, an extended ISO-8601 Time string, with an optional timezone offset.
    GsonTemporalAdapters.TimestampAdapter
    Adapter for Temporal.Timestamp, a scalar type that represents the number of seconds elapsed since 1970-01-01T00:00Z.
    Temporal
    Namespace for all the Date/Time related types.
    Temporal.Date
    Represents a valid extended ISO-8601 Date string, with an optional timezone offset.
    Temporal.DateTime
    Represents a valid extended ISO-8601 DateTime string.
    Temporal.Time
    Represents a valid extended ISO-8601 Time string, with an optional timezone offset.
    Temporal.Timestamp
    The Temporal.Timestamp scalar type represents the number of seconds that have elapsed since 1970-01-01T00:00Z.
